---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Nosotros | Plantilla 1">
<section class="bg-primary py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-base md:px-gutter grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter items-center">
<div class="text-on-primary reveal">
<h1 class="font-display-hero-mobile md:font-display-hero text-display-hero-mobile md:text-display-hero mb-6">
                    Impulsamos el crecimiento de tu marca trabajando en equipo.
                </h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg opacity-90 max-w-xl mb-10">
                    Nuestro compromiso es ir más allá de tus metas, forjando alianzas duraderas cimentadas en la transparencia y los triunfos mutuos.
                </p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<button class="bg-on-primary text-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold btn-magnetic press-effect">
                        <span class="icon-wrap">Nuestra Historia</span>
                    </button>
<button class="border-2 border-on-primary text-on-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-on-primary hover:text-primary transition-all btn-magnetic">
                        <span class="icon-wrap">Servicios</span>
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative mt-12 md:mt-0 reveal">
<div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-white/10 rounded-card blur-2xl"></div>
<img alt="Equipo trabajando" class="relative z-10 w-full rounded-card shadow-2xl" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCQhPEMMIcG4hW_a1hwRUCZbB6U011aYxBNG6rY_Wlm0kLNNxgNBuaZQK2W43MWAdxsIFeJYhACgabnvUUnSsyWL0-nrqiRYX2Ui3MSA7xgEzpBZHaT4sd-QmisarvyAZlU2UxGFMFBb0PDkw8MM7YodinZHkhpF331gfHKMEFT9A2srJO4QsyiX8AnamTwk_Nosqrz92z1UgUOYnS-ROZWMOxxq6yoWgqVdA6u-bhcgrsZ9lnBT24GjhIJG-iVejSSjbOq7wFHksbI">
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-base md:px-gutter grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
<div class="lg:col-span-5 relative reveal">
<img alt="Liderazgo creativo" class="w-full h-auto rounded-card shadow-xl border-4 border-white" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDwKFIrrQy6l4HevDOlZIakGLDpej8j1gVs_wOQVLKp8w_lk2pi7YnE68Oq-hxvmfYm28agDkMRbfQJ3Q7jCgPVoIKgUdrtba4HL6PPxLTgvBDCfuLbpunBVDd_c3BvK_Em21m4HiCEjARo-2WSyFqw7IG0v-CpFOhUXlwNVkMgs42cs2w1XnaIs0yQHu_xYsObjOOjyGKoaNORKPRpfZPDwqIU0k8vV6V0yB7wgFNWwk2PiKq8k49uEFvAu7hONvLa6KlVkxayUGHO">
<div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 hidden md:block">
<div class="bg-primary text-on-primary p-8 rounded-card shadow-lg max-w-[240px]">
<span class="font-display-hero-mobile text-display-hero-mobile block">10+</span>
<span class="font-body-md text-body-md">Años transformando marcas digitales</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-7 reveal">
<span class="text-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">Nuestra Esencia</span>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg-mobile md:font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-8">
                    El motor que impulsa nuestra agencia
                </h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                    Vivimos para detonar el máximo rendimiento de tu negocio en internet. No somos solo una agencia, somos tu socio estratégico. Entendemos que cada clic cuenta y cada interacción es una oportunidad para brillar. Nuestra metodología combina datos rigurosos con una creatividad desbordante para asegurar que tu marca no solo sea vista, sino recordada.
                </p>
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm px-10 py-5 rounded-full btn-magnetic press-effect shadow-md shadow-primary/20">
                    <span class="icon-wrap">Hablemos de tu proyecto</span>
                </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-base md:px-gutter text-center">
<div class="w-16 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto mb-10"></div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg-mobile md:font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-8">
                Quiénes Somos
            </h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed mb-8">
                Nuestra misión es maximizar tu presencia online de forma contundente. Creemos en el poder de las ideas bien ejecutadas y en la tecnología como facilitador del crecimiento humano. VibrantAgency nació de la necesidad de ofrecer soluciones digitales que realmente muevan la aguja del éxito empresarial, sin complicaciones y con total transparencia.
            </p>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16">
<div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold text-headline-md font-headline-md mb-2">500+</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Proyectos</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold text-headline-md font-headline-md mb-2">98%</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Retención</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold text-headline-md font-headline-md mb-2">24/7</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Soporte</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-primary font-bold text-headline-md font-headline-md mb-2">15</div>
<div class="text-on-surface-variant font-label-sm text-label-sm uppercase">Países</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-section-padding-mobile md:py-section-padding-desktop">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-base md:px-gutter">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg-mobile md:font-headline-lg text-headline-lg-mobile md:text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4">
                        Conoce a nuestros expertos
                    </h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg italic text-primary">
                        El talento gana partidos, pero el trabajo en equipo y la inteligencia ganan campeonatos.
                    </p>
</div>
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-label-sm text-label-sm px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold btn-magnetic press-effect shadow-md shadow-primary/20 whitespace-nowrap">
                    <span class="icon-wrap">Agenda una cita</span>
                </button>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
<div class="group cursor-pointer stagger-fade">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-card mb-4 bg-on-surface aspect-square">
<img alt="Alex Rivera" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCw68RandWuA-Cm66imlHO-2YaWcYkyGI0n__B4_S0gAi0BT9TZlemaiVNzbqp7ZnAtuiNhTc1WWoidxFicwQzbSRsr89x0zScYYenAWvffaK-8hyCxkJ-KrK7evS0H4ppjC-sokzLd51aYZCAND9vZyT2isoWP-HIPjO-l815HFdkD6RFfB7eTk4xHmxIYOaFZs0SzkKD4y3RF-YA_yvjJalYx9w6JeDn5hyQqMJmJZh5tSU-ey2ZltKzF7vgY__uxG8SKks2sRaFI">
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Alex Rivera</h3>
<p class="text-primary font-body-md text-body-md">Director Creativo</p>
</div>
<div class="group cursor-pointer stagger-fade">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-card mb-4 bg-on-surface aspect-square">
<img alt="Elena Gómez" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCw68RandWuA-Cm66imlHO-2YaWcYkyGI0n__B4_S0gAi0BT9TZlemaiVNzbqp7ZnAtuiNhTc1WWoidxFicwQzbSRsr89x0zScYYenAWvffaK-8hyCxkJ-KrK7evS0H4ppjC-sokzLd51aYZCAND9vZyT2isoWP-HIPjO-l815HFdkD6RFfB7eTk4xHmxIYOaFZs0SzkKD4y3RF-YA_yvjJalYx9w6JeDn5hyQqMJmJZh5tSU-ey2ZltKzF7vgY__uxG8SKks2sRaFI">
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Elena Gómez</h3>
<p class="text-primary font-body-md text-body-md">Estratega SEO</p>
</div>
<div class="group cursor-pointer stagger-fade">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-card mb-4 bg-on-surface aspect-square">
<img alt="Marc Costa" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCw68RandWuA-Cm66imlHO-2YaWcYkyGI0n__B4_S0gAi0BT9TZlemaiVNzbqp7ZnAtuiNhTc1WWoidxFicwQzbSRsr89x0zScYYenAWvffaK-8hyCxkJ-KrK7evS0H4ppjC-sokzLd51aYZCAND9vZyT2isoWP-HIPjO-l815HFdkD6RFfB7eTk4xHmxIYOaFZs0SzkKD4y3RF-YA_yvjJalYx9w6JeDn5hyQqMJmJZh5tSU-ey2ZltKzF7vgY__uxG8SKks2sRaFI">
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Marc Costa</h3>
<p class="text-primary font-body-md text-body-md">Lead Developer</p>
</div>
<div class="group cursor-pointer stagger-fade">
<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-card mb-4 bg-on-surface aspect-square">
<img alt="Sofía Méndez" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCw68RandWuA-Cm66imlHO-2YaWcYkyGI0n__B4_S0gAi0BT9TZlemaiVNzbqp7ZnAtuiNhTc1WWoidxFicwQzbSRsr89x0zScYYenAWvffaK-8hyCxkJ-KrK7evS0H4ppjC-sokzLd51aYZCAND9vZyT2isoWP-HIPjO-l815HFdkD6RFfB7eTk4xHmxIYOaFZs0SzkKD4y3RF-YA_yvjJalYx9w6JeDn5hyQqMJmJZh5tSU-ey2ZltKzF7vgY__uxG8SKks2sRaFI">
</div>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Sofía Méndez</h3>
<p class="text-primary font-body-md text-body-md">Growth Manager</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</Layout>
